# Web app — Zugvögel

- Player UI: German default + English (`@nuxtjs/i18n`, `web/locales/`). Admin/crew: English hardcoded.
- Game state lives on the server; client reflects `/api/me`.
- Use `web/shared/` for scoring, Zod schemas, types — never import server code from `app/`.
- Pixel components under `app/components/pixel/`; prefer existing tokens in `pixel-theme.css`.
